{"tid":915616,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突有巨額落注賭梅根懷孖胎 博彩公司封盤：應係內幕料","createTime":"2018-11-25T06:18:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T07:02:36.000Z","uid":28765,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"69cbd6193e8aa2477aee1e60742e1d630c6b1233","tid":915616,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T06:18:22.000Z","msg":"英國薩塞克斯公爵夫人梅根宣佈懷孕後，外界都在猜測新一名皇室寶寶的性別。愛爾蘭一間博彩公司表示，周五突然收到「前所未有」的巨額投注賭梅根懷上孖胎，估計對方或有內幕消息，決定周六即時封盤。<br />\nPaddy Power發言人指，有人下重注賭梅根懷孖胎後，賠率即時被壓低，由本來一賠五變成大熱。他表示：「我們要暫停落注，在皇室宣佈兩人婚事及懷孕前，我們亦遇過幾乎相同的下注模式。」<br />\n發言人續指該筆下注是「史無前例」的多，「自那天開始的一系列下注，令我們相信那位投注者－－或是內幕人士－－可能知道得比我們更多。」<br />\n英國國民保健服務（NHS）資料顯示，35歲後懷孕的女性，懷上異卵雙胞胎的機會更高。<br />\nPaddy Power亦有開盤賭哈里及梅根首位寶寶的名字，目前「戴安娜」仍是大熱之選，賠率為一賠八。<br />\n英國《每日鏡報》  <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181125/58955105\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181125%2F58955105&d=u3JrMCpuOh9JSbHLS7pmfvjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=e54224e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181125%2F58955105&h=a591e2df\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181125/58955105</a>"},{"pid":"8565165125e09f9b5f2fbf73e8bfcc8acb0035a4","tid":915616,"uid":11148,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T06:33:15.000Z","msg":"力架打孖上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1f499ee72a570d3094fbfcce8879179bb18799a","tid":915616,"uid":73,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T06:40:44.000Z","msg":"nigga 本身就一樣樣<br />\n孖唔孖冇分別"},{"pid":"8c96cd8593e20d481b2c2a607d66a452e8934fc9","tid":915616,"uid":121580,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T06:41:00.000Z","msg":"on9封盤<br />\n照收除返比例賠好似馬會咁<b